lead_paragraph: Kelsey Plum scored 44 points and grabbed a career-high nine rebounds as No. 15 Washington rolled to a 94-64 victory over Seattle on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Plum Scores 44 Points; No. 15 Washington Women Beat Seattle
